After upgrading a GApps-enabled instance from June to July, for an hour or two after upgrading, no non-Google users can log in.

1) ssh to a Unicorn instance.
2) Run /sw/studio/studio-fireball-105.x-stable-pwyatt/install/clean-install-gapps-studio.sh
3) Populate some non-GApps users.

